{"tid":1448640,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［諗到新對策］而家可以將所有責任比晒警察 再逼政府立獨立調查會","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:40:12.000Z","uid":301632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5bd1dba2fc7703f3201ba505341ed7e409d8fae5","tid":1448640,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4uaqWK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4uaqWK.png&h=6356a31e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都知正話now影到有狗扮示威者<br />\n咁樣代表 <span style=\"color: red;\">有好多其他case都係啲狗嘅「臥底」行為</span><br />\n即係話呢排好多拋磚、縱火等等 部分<span style=\"color: blue;\">市民</span>討厭嘅「激進行為」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">都有可能係啲狗做嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁文宣可以做嘢 <span style=\"color: red;\">將所有嘢推晒落差佬度</span><br />\n市民睇度啲訊息後 例如懷疑警察嘅圖<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自然對差佬更反感</span></span><br />\n差佬冇做過嘅 自然嬲鳩 覺得無辜啦<br />\n就會屌晒鬼 好大可能忍唔住要同上面講 <br />\n<br />\n咁樣做 可以令<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">差佬本身</span></span>都想成立獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 還自己清白<br />\n當然佢地可以利用監警會<br />\n但到時如果調查不公 我地再用一波輿論抗議 再要求成立（呢個後續）<br />\n但起碼會有調查工作 到時唔滿意再進一步逼使 有如撤回/暫緩<br />\n希望大家考慮下呢個方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推推佢討論一下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E24BmzJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE24BmzJ.png&h=eadec8c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RPk8W74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRPk8W74.png&h=3cba8b75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e6915176311791b6cf3844989796594b8b0ae1c","tid":1448640,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf1d52690e764fd04ff14227ce861faf08f8dcb","tid":1448640,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrM8cHn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrM8cHn.png&h=a129d4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfieSHo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfieSHo.png&h=a6cd5994&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56de1aede03ad88366f5b65c2df0dd1a8fb7bd91","tid":1448640,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4092ef8e440e8b875b9cc44fd39ffa910b3f7c2f","tid":1448640,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:10:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"19a66b474f720f3352d1cea05668551a86b966c6","tid":1448640,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"036668074c4c64c89da2de0e4330a2fdf8f3c451","tid":1448640,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:48:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c3f7a88c980bf6e2353b1ae28fb73b7e344a3768","tid":1448640,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:11:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4dd28382b51582a4d66391d0f7211df7dd843a02","tid":1448640,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:20:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0689b5fb6b0dbcaffa36b1bfca5cf48fbc691133","tid":1448640,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}